'''潘丹尼斯城堡'''（{{lang-en|Pendennis Castle}}，{{lang-kw|Kastel Penndinas}}）<ref>[http://www.magakernow.org.uk/default.aspx?page=520 Place-names in the Standard Written Form (SWF)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.magakernow.org.uk/default.aspx?page=520 |date=20130515091028 }} : [http://www.magakernow.org.uk/idoc.ashx?docid=79ba408d-7c02-499e-8cd6-b18dd48de58d&version=-1 List of place-names agreed by the MAGA Signage Panel] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515071635/http://www.magakernow.org.uk/idoc.ashx?docid=79ba408d-7c02-499e-8cd6-b18dd48de58d&version=-1 |date=2013-05-15 }}.</ref>是位於[[英國|英國]][[康沃爾郡|康沃爾郡]][[法爾茅斯|法爾茅斯]]的一座城堡，修建於1539年至1545年亨利八世統治時期。在英國內戰時期，潘丹尼斯城堡曾是西部保王黨最後的據點。
